Gemini on terminal

ai [OPTIONS] promt


OPTIONS

	-i	--init		Create the config file for this aplication
	-o			Configure the default promt for the AI, changing the behaviour of the AI
	-t	--API_KEY	Configure the API-KEY
	-s	--save		Toggle the history of chats
	-r	--read		Show the history
		--s2t		Speech to text ui
		--configure	Open the configuration file